rding%20to%20CBI%20sources%2C%20the%20investigation%20will%20proceed%20through%20four%20phases%2C%20scrutinizing%20every%20aspect%20from%20the%20creation%20and%20printing%20of%20exam%20papers%20to%20their%20distribution%20across%20various%20examination%20centres%20nationwide.%20The%20National%20Testing%20Agency%20(NTA)%2C%20responsible%20for%20conducting%20these%20exams%2C%20has%20stringent%20protocols%20in%20place%20to%20maintain%20confidentiality%2C%20making%20any%20breach%20a%20matter%20of%20grave%20concern.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECBI%20officials%20are%20also%20focusing%20on%20individuals%20directly%20involved%20in%20the%20preparation%2C%20printing%2C%20transportation%2C%20and%20secure%20storage%20of%20exam%20papers%20before%20the%20commencement%20of%20exams.%20These%20roles%20entail%20safeguarding%20the%20papers%20until%20just%20hours%20before%20the%20tests%20begin%2C%20highlighting%20potential%20points%20of%20vulnerability%20in%20the%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUtilising%20a%20database%20of%201%2C000%20names%20and%20phone%20numbers%20compiled%20during%20previous%20investigations%2C%20CBI%20is%20tracing%20those%20who%20may%20be%20connected%20to%20the%20leaks.%20This%20data%2C%20obtained%20from%20multiple%20cases%20including%20Vyapam%2C%20aids%20in%20identifying%20suspects%20and%20establishing%20communication%20patterns%20that%20could%20reveal%20the%20nexus%20behind%20the%20leaks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20controversy%20erupted%20after%20an%20unusually%20high%20number%20of%20students%20scored%20a%20perfect%20720%20in%20the%20NEET-UG%20exam.%20Initially%20attributed%20to%20grace%20marks%20due%20to%20a%20faulty%20question%20and%20logistical%20issues%2C%20subsequent%20investigations%20by%20Bihar%20Police%20uncovered%20a%20different%20aspect%3A%20the%20exam%20paper%20had%20been%20leaked%20to%20select%20candidates%20a%20day%20before%20the%20exam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJust%20days%20later%2C%20the%20Education%20Ministry%20cancelled%20the%20UGC-NET%20exam%20claiming%20that%20the%20%26quot%3Bintegrity%20of%20the%20exam%20has%20been%20compromised%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BTo%20ensure%20the%20highest%20level%20of%20transparency%20and%20sanctity%20of%20the%20examination%20process%2C%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Education%2C%20Government%20of%20India%20has%20decided%20that%20the%20UGC-NET%20June%202024%20Examination%20be%20cancelled%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20ministry%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENearly%2024%20lakh%20students%20had%20appeared%20for%20the%20NEET-UG%202024%20for%20undergraduate%20medical%20courses.%20Over%209%20lakh%20students%20took%20the%20UGC-NET%20exam%2C%20which%20assess%20the%20eligibility%20for%20'Assistant%20Professor'%20for%20'Junior%20Research%20Fellowship%20and%20Assistant%20Professor'%20roles%20in%20universities%20and%20colleges%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStudent%20protests%20have%20been%20raging%20across%20the%20country%20since%20amplified%20by%20the%20Opposition%2C%20and%20the%20matter%20has%20snowballed%20into%20a%20huge%20political%20row.%20Cases%20were%20also%20filed%20in%20courts%2C%20including%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20which%20has%20come%20down%20heavily%20on%20the%20NTA.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20chief%20of%20the%20National%20Testing%20Agency%20or%20NTA%2C%20which%20conducted%20the%20exams%2C%20has%20been%20fired.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719227280000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fm6tes5mg_neet-protest_625x300_24_June_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fneet-exam-row-net-nta-probe-4-phase-probe-1-000-phone-numbers-cbi-plan-to-crack-paper-leak-cases-5958970%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Investigating%20the%20alleged%20paper%20leaks%20of%20the%20NEET%20and%20NET%20exams%2C%20the%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20(CBI)%20has%20dispatched%20teams%20to%20Bihar%20and%20Gujarat's%20Godhra%20to%20gather%20evidence.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2