o.%20At%20this%20rate%2C%20the%20end%20of%20the%20conflict%20may%20come%20soon.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGroup%20Captain%20Tufail%20gives%20the%20Pakistani%20account%20of%20Mirage%20strikes%20and%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20Mirage-2000s%20scored%20at%20least%20five%20successful%20laser-guided%20bomb%20hits%20on%20forward%20dumping%20sites%20and%20posts.%20During%20the%20last%20days%20of%20operations%20which%20ended%20on%2012%20July%2C%20it%20was%20clear%20that%20delivery%20accuracy%20had%20improved%20considerably.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20June%2024%2C%20a%20Jaguar%20pilot%20was%20tasked%20to%20bomb%20point%204388%20but%20mistakenly%20lazered%20at%20an%20army%20base%20in%20Gulteri%20in%20Pakistan%20Occupied%20Kashmir%20where%20then%20Pakistan%20Army%20Chief%20General%20Pervez%20Musharraf%20and%20Prime%20Minister%20Nawaz%20Sharif%20were%20present.%20The%20IAF%20pilot%20was%20stopped%20by%20his%20senior%20officials%20from%20bombing%20the%20camp%20and%20avoiding%20a%20major%20escalation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBattle%20Damage%20Assessment%20(BDA)%20is%20part%20of%20an%20airstrike.%20Footage%20shared%20by%20the%20IAF%20a%20few%20years%20ago%20shows%20the%20damage%20precision%20strikes%20on%20Tiger%20Hill%20did.%20After%20bombing%20Tiger%20Hill%2C%20Wing%20Commander%20Nambiar%20filmed%20the%20area%20to%20assess%20enemy%20presence.%20%26quot%3BThe%20entire%20squadron%20was%20gathered%20around%20the%20TV%20as%20the%20tape%20was%20rewound%20and%20played%20back.%20Clearly%20visible%20on%20the%20tape%20were%20four%20enemy%20soldiers%20rushing%20across%20the%20screen%20a%20few%20seconds%20before%20the%20bomb%20got%20to%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20writes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20piece%20of%20rock%20from%20Tiger%20Hill%20at%20Prime%20Ministers%20museum%20in%20Delhi%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22A%20piece%20of%20rock%20from%20Tiger%20Hill%20at%20Prime%20Ministers%20museum%20in%20Delhi%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%