tchers%20but%20a%20significant%20portion%20of%20cinema-goers%20looking%20for%20that%20new%20thing%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BThey%20should%20be%20able%20to%20capture%20those%20audiences%20that%20are%20loyal%20to%20concerts.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a86521ca-1b6d-46dd-8bf7-56f7a1df1c51%5C%22%3ENetflix%20could%20rescue%20struggling%3Cstrong%3E%20shopping%20malls%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20shuttered%20Sears%20store%20at%20Lycoming%20Mall%20in%20Pennsylvania.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66786f6ed1c84a0eaca6efb2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223334%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20shuttered%20Sears%20store%20at%20Lycoming%20Mall%20in%20Pennsylvania.%3Cp%3ESOPA%20Images%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ENetflix%20investing%20in%20shopping%20malls%20might%20seem%20at%20odds%20with%20headlines%20announcing%20the%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbank-financing-urban-planning-pandemic-retail-apocalypse-vacant-storefront-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eretail%20apocalypse%3C%2Fa%3E.%26quot%3B%20However%2C%20Steinberg%20said%20there's%20still%20money%20to%20be%20made%20in%20these%20establishments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMalls%20are%20certainly%20having%20problems%20in%20a%20large%20component%20of%20the%20country%2C%20but%20it's%20a%20very%20low-cost%20way%20of%20getting%20large%20amounts%20of%20foot%20traffic%2C%26quot%3B%20Steinberg%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20Netflix%20would%20likely%20get%20more%20foot%20traffic%20in%20a%20mall%20than%20if%20they%20built%20stand-alone%20shops.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEven%20though%20numbers%20might%20be%20softer%20than%20in%20the%20past%2C%20these%20are%20two%20of%20the%20biggest%20and%20most%20frequented%20malls%20in%20the%20country%2C%26quot%3B%20Steinberg%20added%2C%20referring%20to%20King%20