uo%20motu%20(on%20its%20own)%20cognizance%20of%20the%20issue%20of%20illegal%20and%20unauthorised%20hawkers%20and%20vendors%20in%20the%20city.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Monday%2C%20the%20bench%20said%20while%20it%20knows%20the%20problem%20is%20large%2C%20the%20state%20and%20other%20authorities%2C%20including%20the%20civic%20body%2C%20cannot%20just%20leave%20it%20at%20that%20and%20called%20for%20some%20drastic%20action.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20the%20prime%20minister%20or%20some%20VVIPs%20come%2C%20the%20streets%20and%20footpaths%20are%20immediately%20cleared...and%20it%20stays%20so%20till%20they%20are%20here.%20How%20is%20it%20done%20then%3F%20Why%20can't%20it%20be%20done%20for%20everyone%20else%3F%20Citizens%20are%20ratepayers...they%20need%20to%20have%20a%20clear%20footpath%20and%20safe%20place%20to%20walk%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFootpath%20and%20a%20safe%20place%20to%20walk%20is%20a%20fundamental%20right.%20We%20tell%20our%20children%20to%20walk%20on%20footpaths%20but%20if%20there%20is%20no%20footpath%20left%20to%20walk%20on%2C%20what%20do%20we%20tell%20our%20children%3F%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20years%20together%2C%20the%20authorities%20have%20been%20saying%20they%20are%20working%20on%20the%20issue%2C%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20state%20has%20to%20do%20something%20drastically.%20It%20cannot%20be%20that%20the%20authorities%20are%20perpetually%20just%20wondering%20what%20to%20do%20and%20working%20on%20it.%20There%20seems%20to%20be%20a%20lack%20of%20will%2C%20because%20where%20there%20is%20a%20will%20there%20is%20always%20a%20way%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20high%20court%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESenior%20counsel%20SU%20Kamdar%2C%20appearing%20for%20the%20Brihanmumbai%20Municipal%20Corporation%20(BMC)%2C%20said%20periodic%20action%20is%20taken%20against%20such%20vendors%20and%20hawkers%20but%20they%20keep%20coming%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20BMC%20wa