Fpaytm-eyes-expansion-in-travel-ties-up-with-skyscanner-google-flights-124062400541_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%204%20Engineers%20Leaked%20A%20Key%20Government%20Exam%20In%20UP%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAmid%20the%20furore%20over%20the%20alleged%20paper%20leak%20in%20medical%20entrance%20exam%20NEET%2C%20police%20investigation%20reveals%20the%20extensive%20conspiracy%20and%20planning%20in%20another%20leaked%20exam.%20The%20qualifying%20exams%20for%20the%20post%20of%20Review%20Officer%2FAssistant%20Review%20Officer%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20held%20on%20February%2011%2C%20was%20cancelled%20amid%20allegations%20of%20paper%20leak.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20allegations%20of%20the%20questions%20being%20leaked%20surfaced%2C%20administration%20strongly%20denied%20it.%20%26quot%3BThere%20was%20no%20paper%20leak.%20I%20completely%20refute%20it.%20There%20was%20negligence%20on%20behalf%20of%20the%20centre%20invigilator%20who%20opened%20a%20bundle%20of%20exam%20question%20paper%20in%20the%20control%20room%20instead%20of%20the%20examination%20hall%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Ghazipur%20District%20Magistrate%20Aryaka%20Akhauri.%20Four%20months%20later%2C%20she%20has%20been%20proved%20wrong.%20Her%20investigation%20hadn't%20covered%20the%20meticulous%20plan%2C%20partly%20devised%20at%20a%20printing%20press%20in%20Bhopal%2C%20950%20km%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMore%20than%2010%20Lakh%20students%20had%20appeared%20for%20the%20examination%20that%20was%20cancelled.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Investigation%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInvestigations%20revealed%20that%20the%20exam%20paper%20leak%20took%20place%20at%20the%20Bishop%20Johnson%20Girl's%20High%20School%20and%20College%20in%20Prayagraj.%20Later%2C%20a%20Special%20Task%20Force%20found%20that%20the%20paper%20was%20leaked%20from%20the%20printing%20press%20as%20well.%20At%20the%20core%20of%20the%20leak%20were%20four%20engineers%20-%20Rajiv%20Nayan%20Mishra%2C%20Sunil%20Raghuvanshi%2C%20Vishal%20Dubey%2C%20and%20Subhash%20Prakash%20.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20second%20leak%2C%20at%20the%20school%2C%20happened%20a%20few%20hours%20before%20the%20exam%2C%20sources%20said.%20Arpit%20Vineet%20Yashwant%2C%20who%20was%20overseeing%20the%20examination%2C%20took%20pictures%20of%20the%20question%20paper%20at%206.30%20am%20on%20the%20morning%20of%20the%20exam.%20Five%20people%2C%20including%20Arpit%2C%20have%20been%20arrested%20in%20this%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPaper%20Leak%20From%20The%20Printing%20Press%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20leak%20took%20place%20at%20the%20printing%20press%20in%20Bhopal%20where%20the%20exam%20paper%20was%20printed.%20Rajiv%20Nayan%20Mishra%2C%20one%20of%20the%20masterminds%20of%20the%20UP%20police%20exam%20paper%20leak%2C%20plotted%20it%20with%20a%20printing%20press%20employee%2C%20Sunil%20Raghuvanshi%2C%20Vishal%20Dubey%20and%20Subhash%20Praksh.%20All%20of%20them%20have%20engineering%20degrees.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERajiv%20Nayan%20Mishra%20met%20Sunil%20Raghuvanshi%20through%20Vishal%20Dubey.%20Sunil%20Raghuvanshi%20and%20Vishal%20Dubey%20studied%20together%20in%20engineering%20college.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Sunil%20worked%20at%20the%20printing%20press%2C%20Vishal%20and%20Subhash%20used%20to%20arrange%20the%20admission%20of%20students%20into%20engineering%20colleges.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Vishal%20realised%20that%20his%20classmate%20worked%20at%20the%20printing%20place%2C%20he%20informed%20Rajiv%20Mishra.%20They%20bribed%20Sunil%20Raghuvanshi%20into%20helping%20them%20and%20handing%20them%20the%20question%20paper%20for%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20RO%2FARO%20question%20paper%20came%20to%20the%20printing%20press%2C%20Sunil%20informed%20the%20others.%20He%20demanded%20Rs%2010%20lakh%20to%20give%20them%20access%20to%20the%20paper.%20But%20he%20had%20a%20condition%20-%20the%20candidates%20should%20be%20made%20to%20read%20the%20paper%20in%20front%20of%20him%20so%20it%20didn't%20go%20viral.%20Rajiv%20Mishra%2C%20Sunil%20Raghuvanshi%20and%20another%20accomplice%2C%20Subhash%20Prakash%2C%20agreed%20to%20the%20terms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20Engineers%20Engineered%20the%20Leak%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInvestigating%20officer%20Amit%20Srivastava%2C%20a%20member%20of%20the%20Varanasi%20unit%20of%20the%20special%20task%20force%2C%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BAll%20of%20them%20were%20engineers%2C%20they%20were%20smart%20and%20technically%20very%20sound.%20They%20meticulously%20planned%20the%20paper%20leak.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVishal%20Dubey%20had%20told%20Sunil%20that%20to%20identify%20the%20RO%2FARO%20paper%2C%20he%20needed%20to%20look%20for%20two%20sets%20of%20paper%20with%20140%20and%2040%20questions%20in%20them%20respectively.%20He%20added%20that%20the%20question%20paper%20would%20also%20include%20questions%20on%20UP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESunil%20Raghuvanshi%20kept%20looking%20for%20an%20opportunity.%20If%20a%20question%20paper%20is%20damaged%20during%20printing%2C%20it%20is%20kept%20aside%20and%20destroyed%20using%20a%20paper%20shredder.%20On%20February%203%2C%20Sunil%20was%20present%20at%20the%20printing%20press%20for%20machine%20repairs.%20Spotting%20the%20question%20paper%20in%20the%20press%2C%20he%20took%20it%20along%20with%20a%20machine%20part%2C%20pretending%20he%20was%20going%20to%20fix%20it.%20He%20took%20the%20papers%20home%20and%20informed%20the%20others.%20The%20group%20decided%20that%20on%20February%208%20-%20three%20days%20before%20the%20exam%20-%20candidates%20would%20be%20taken%20to%20a%20hotel%2C%20Komal%2C%20and%20shown%20the%20paper%20for%20Rs%2012%20lakh%20each.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESunil%20reached%20the%20Hotel%20with%20six%20copies%20of%20two%20sets%20of%20question%20papers.%20Subhash%20Prakash%20solved%20the%20paper%20along%20with%20a%20helper%20and%20the%20students%20were%20made%20to%20memorise%20the%20answers.%20Two%20other%20accomplices%2C%20Vivek%20Upadhyay%20and%20Amarjeet%20Sharma%2C%20brought%20the%20candidates%20to%20the%20Hotel.%20Vivek%20belongs%20from%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20and%20Amarjeet%20is%20from%20Bihar%2C%20they%20acted%20as%20agents%20who%20arranged%20the%20candidates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESubhash%20Prakash%20was%20himself%20a%20candidate%20for%20the%20RO%2FARO%20exam.%20The%20police%20found%20question%20papers%20from%20his%20phone%20and%20the%20serial%20numbers%20were%20identical%20to%20those%20viral%20on%20social%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20turned%20out%20that%20Rajiv%20Nayan%20Mishra%2C%20greedy%20for%20more%20money%2C%20had%20shared%20images%20of%20the%20question%20paper%20with%20Ravi%20Attri%20-%20the%20mastermind%20of%20the%20UP%20Police%20constable%20paper%20leak.%20After%20this%2C%20the%20paper%20went%20viral%20on%20social%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERajiv%20Mishra%2C%20the%20kingpin%20of%20this%20operation%20had%20earlier%20been%20involved%20in%20other%20crimes%20as%20well.%20His%20girlfriend%20Shivani%20was%20also%20a%20part%20of%20the%20operation%20and%20looked%20after%20the%20money%20transactions%2C%20according%20to%20the%20police.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESix%20people%20have%20been%20arrested%20and%20investigations%20continue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EUP%20Police%20Constable%20Exam%20Leak%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20similar%20operation%20was%20arranged%20by%20Rajiv%20Mishra%20and%20Ravi%20Attri%20to%20leak%20the%20UP%20Police%20Constable%20exam%2C%20held%20days%20after%20the%20RO%2FARO%20Exam.%20In%20that%2C%20an%20employee%20of%20the%20transportation%20company%20helped%20the%20masterminds%20arrange%20the%20question%20papers%20with%20a%20safe-breaking%20expert%20from%20Bihar.%20Both%20Ravi%20Attri%20and%20Rajiv%20Mishra%20are%20in%20Meerut%20Jail.%20In%20the%20UP%20Police%20Constable%20exam%2C%20more%20than%2047%20lakh%20aspirants%20appeared%20for%2060%2C000%20job%20vacancies.%20The%20examination%20was%20cancelled%20after%20paper%20leak%20allegations.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719221040000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%