go%20back%20to%20jail...%20as%20he%20did%20after%20the%20Supreme%20Court's%20interim%20release%20(to%20campaign%20for%20the%20election)%2C%26quot%3B%20senior%20advocate%20Abhishek%20Singhvi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20referring%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Farvind-kejriwal-gets-interim-bail-till-june-1-in-liquor-policy-case-5631576%23pfrom%3Dhome-ndtv_bigstory%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMr%20Kejriwal's%20release%20last%20month%20-%20allowed%20by%20the%20top%20court%3C%2Fa%3E%20-%20to%20campaign%20for%20his%20party%20and%20the%20Congress-led%20INDIA%20bloc%20in%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%2C%20in%20which%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's%20BJP%20was%20pegged%20back%20and%20forced%20to%20rely%20on%20its%20allies%20to%20form%20the%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Singhvi%20also%20referred%20to%20the%20top%20court's%20order%20granting%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20that%20interim%20bail%2C%20in%20which%20it%20acknowledged%20the%20AAP%20leader%20is%20not%20a%20%26quot%3Bhabitual%20offender%26quot%3B%20and%20has%20no%20criminal%20antecedents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhy%20can't%20I%20be%20free%20in%20the%20interim%3F%20I%20have%20a%20judgment%20in%20my%20favour...%26quot%3B%20he%20continued%2C%20responding%20to%20the%20court%20suggesting%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20be%20patient%20for%2024-48%20hours%20till%20the%20High%20Court%20reads%20its%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%3C%2Fstrong%3E%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Farvind-kejriwal-bail-order-cant-be-a-more-perverse-order-probe-agency-on-arvind-kejriwal-bail-5937726%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENear%20Release%2C%20Kejriwal's%20Bail%20Paused%20Till%20New%20Court%20Decision%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20we%20pass%20order%20now%2C%20we%20will%20prejudge%20the%20issue.%20This%20is%20not%20a%20subordinate%20court...%26quot%3B%20he%20was%20told.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kejriwal's%20side%20argued%20strenuously%20the%20stay%20order%20should%20not%20be%20allowed%20to%20stand%20because%20the%20lower%20court's%20order%20had%20not%20been%20released%20when%20the%20High%20Court%20listed%20the%20ED's%20challenge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20was%20only%20an%20oral%20direction%20to%20not%20give%20effect%20to%20the%20bail%20order...%26quot%3B%20his%20camp%20pointed%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20(Mr%20Kejriwal's%20regular%20bail%20order)%20is%20a%20discretionary%20order%20passed%20by%20a%20trial%20court%20for%20a%20person%20who%20was%20(already)%20released%20by%20this%20honourable%20court%2C%26quot%3B%20senior%20advocate%20Vikram%20Chaudhary%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E%26quot%3BPerverse%20Order%20Can%20Be%20Stayed%26quot%3B%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ED%2C%20however%2C%20stressed%20that%20a%20%26quot%3Bperverse%26quot%3B%2C%20or%20incorrect%2C%20order%20can%20and%20should%20be%20stayed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20federal%20agency%20earlier%20argued%20the%20trial%20court's%20order%20-%20giving%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20bail%20-%20is%20%26quot%3B...%20completely%20flawed.%20The%20court%20said%20there%20was%20no%20direct%20proof.%20That's%20a%20wrong%20statement%20by%20the%20court.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20showed%20material%20but%20nothing%20(was)%20considered.%20There%20are%20two%20ways%20bail%20can%20be%20cancelled%3B%20one%20is%2C%20if%20relevant%20facts%20are%20not%20considered.%20That%20is%20grounds%20for%20cancellation%20of%20bail.%20All%20I%20am%20saying%20is%20'look%20at%20the%20soundness%20of%20the%20order'.%20Bail%20could%20have%20granted%20bail%20but%20not%20like%20this...%26quot%3B%20the%20agency%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20told%20the%20court%20that%2C%20in%20its%20opinion%2C%20the%20twin%20conditions%20for%20grant%20of%20bail%20under%20Section%2045%20of%20the%20Prevention%20of%20Money%20Laundering%20Act%2C%20under%20which%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20has%20been%20charged%2C%