plit%20into%20three%20distinct%20but%20loosely%20connected%20stories.%20Who%20is%20the%20common%20denominator%3F%20A%20nonverbal%20character%20known%20only%20as%20RMF%20(Yorgos%20Stefanakos).%20%E2%80%9CIt%20felt%20like%20a%20subtle%20way%20to%20connect%20the%20three%20stories%20other%20than%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20same%20actors%20play%20a%20different%20character%20in%20each%20story%2C%E2%80%9D%20Lanthimos%20%5B%E2%80%A6%5D%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Michaela%20Zee%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2024%2Fscene%2Fnews%2Fyorgos-lanthimos-kinds-of-kindness-rmf-character-1236044672%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fvariety.com%2F2024%2Fscene%2Fnews%2Fyorgos-lanthimos-kinds-of-kindness-rmf-character-1236044672%2Famp%2F%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2024%2Fscene%2Fnews%2Fyorgos-lanthimos-kinds-of-kindness-rmf-character-1236044672%2Famp%2F%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22What%20Does%20'Ram%20Setu'%20Look%20Like%20From%20Space%3F%20European%20Agency%20Shares%20Pic%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20European%20Space%20Agency%20has%20shared%20an%20image%20of%20the%20Ram%20Setu%20taken%20by%20its%20Copernicus%20Sentinel-2%20satellite.%20Also%20known%20as%20the%20Adam's%20Bridge%2C%20it%20is%20a%20chain%20of%20shoals%20linking%20India%20and%20Sri%20Lanka.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Ram%20Setu%20stretches%2048%20km%20between%20Rameswaram%20Island%2C%20off%20the%20southeast%20coast%20of%20India%2C%20connecting%20the%20Mannar%20Island%20in%20Sri%20Lanka.%20It%20separates%20the%20Gulf%20of%20Mannar%20(south)%2C%20an%20inlet%20of%20the%20Indian%20Ocean%2C%20from%20the%20Palk%20Strait%20(north)%2C%20an%20inlet%20of%20the%20Bay%20of%20Bengal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20there%20are%20numerous%20theories%20about%20how%20the%20bridge%20was%20formed%2C%20geologic%20evidence%20suggests%20that%20these%20limestone%20shoals%20are%20the%20remnants%20of%20land%20that%20once%20linked%20India%20with%20Sri%20Lanka.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20reports%2C%20this%20%26quot%3Bnatural%20bridge%20was%20traversable%20until%20the%2015th%20century%2C%20after%20which%20it%20was%20gradually%20eroded%20by%20storms%20over%20the%20years%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20European%20Space%20Agency%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20noted%20that%20some%20of%20the%20sandbanks%20are%20dry%2C%20while%20the%20sea%20here%20is%20very%20shallow%2C%20only%201%E2%80%9310%20m%20deep%2C%20as%20indicated%20by%20the%20light%20colour%20of%20the%20water.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECovering%20around%20130%20sq%20km%2C%20Mannar%20Island%20is%20connected%20to%20mainland%20Sri%20Lanka%20by%20a%20road%20bridge%20as%20well%20as%20a%20railway%20bridge.%20Both%20of%20them%20are%20visible%20at%20the%20southern%20end%20of%20the%20island.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20Indian%20side%2C%20the%20Rameswaram%20Island%20--%20also%20popular%20as%20Pamban%20Island%20--%20can%20be%20accessed%20via%20the%202-km-long%20Pamban%20Bridge.%20Here%2C%20the%20two%20main%20towns%20are%20Pamban%2C%20on%20the%20western%20edge%2C%20and%20Rameswaram%2C%20which%20is%20around%2010%20km%20east%20of%20Pamban.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20sections%20of%20the%20Ram%20Setu%20are%20part%20of%20protected%20national%20parks%20in%20their%20respective%20countries.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20sand%20dunes%20serve%20as%20breeding%20grounds%20for%20birds%20such%20as%20the%20brown%20noddy%2C%20while%20numerous%20species%20of%20fish%20and%20sea%20grasses%20thrive%20in%20the%20shallow%20waters.%20Sea%20life%20around%20Adam's%20Bridge%20includes%20dolphins%2C%20dugongs%20and%20turtles%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20European%20Space%20Agency%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20year%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20visited%20Arichal%20Munai%2C%20the%20starting%20point%20of%20the%20Ram%20Setu.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719218520000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fg