2%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22European%20regulators%20say%20Apple%20is%20in%20breach%20of%20new%20rules%20with%20its%20App%20Store%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22People%20inside%20an%20Apple%20store.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66712f3be07904901819d741%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22768%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAn%20Apple%20Store%20in%20Towson%2C%20Maryland.%3Cp%3EAndrew%20Harnik%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20European%20Commission%20has%20accused%20Apple%20of%20stifling%20competition%20with%20its%20App%20Store%20policies.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ERegulators%20say%20Apple%20is%20in%20breach%20of%20new%20tech%20rules%20by%20restricting%20alternative%20app%20promotions.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIn%20March%2C%20the%20Commission%20fined%20Apple%201.8%20billion%20euros%2C%20accusing%20it%20of%20abusing%20its%20market%20dominance.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20European%20Commission%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fec.europa.eu%2Fcommission%2Fpresscorner%2Fdetail%2Fen%2FIP_24_3433%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaccused%20Apple%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20stifling%20competition%20with%20its%20App%20Store.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20European%20regulators%20say%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsatya-nadella-sam-altman-openai-apple-microsoft-worried-about-deal-2024-5%3Fmrfhud%3Dtrue%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EApple%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20in%20breach%20of%20new%20tech%20rules%20laid%20out%20in%20the%20Digital%20Markets%20Act%20because%20it%20prevents%20app%20developers%20from%20steering%20customers%20to%20App%20Store%20alternatives.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnder%20the%20European%20rules%2C%20developers%20should%20be%20able%20to%20freely%20inform%20customers%20of%20cheaper%20purchasing%20options%20and%20steer%20them%20toward%20the%20offers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Commission%20says%20Apple's%20business%20terms%20don't%20allow%20developers%20to%20do%20this%2C%20citing%20limits%20on%20communication%20and%20information%20sharing%20within%20the%20app.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMargrethe%20Vestager%2C%20an%20executive%20vice%20president%20of%20the%20European%20Commission%2C%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BOur%20preliminary%20position%20is%20that%20Apple%20does%20not%20fully%20allow%20steering.%20Steering%20is%20key%20to%20ensure%20that%20app%20developers%20are%20less%20dependent%20on%20gatekeepers'%20app%20stores%20and%20for%20consumers%20to%20be%20aware%20of%20better%20offers.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20developers'%20community%20and%20consumers%20are%20eager%20to%20offer%20alternatives%20to%20the%20App%20Store.%20We%20will%20investigate%20to%20ensure%20Apple%20does%20not%20undermine%20these%20efforts%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20regulators%20said%20they'd%20also%20opened%20a%20new%20probe%20into%20Apple's%20contractual%20requirements%20for%20third-party%20app%20developers%20and%20app%20stores.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EApple%20representatives%20didn't%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20Business%20Insider%20made%20outside%20normal%20US%20working%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20an%20Apple%20spokesperson%2C%20Julien%20Trosdorf%2C%20told%20Politico%20that%20the%20company%20was%20%26quot%3Bconfident%20our%20plan%20complies%20with%20the%20law%26quot%3B%20and%20that%20it%20estimated%20%26quot%3Bmore%20than%2099%25%20of%20developers%20would%20pay%20the%20same%20or%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.politico.eu%2Farticle%2Fapple-gets-eu-warning-over-app-store-rules%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DApple%2520is%2520%2522confident%2520our%2520plan%2Csaid%2520company%2520spokesperson%2520Julien%2520Trosdorf.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eless%20in%20fees%20to%20Apple%3C%2Fa%3E%20under%20the%20new%20business%20terms%20we%20created.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20March%2C%20the%20European%20Commission%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessi