tacks-without-evidence-13157924%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20Consensus%20Or%20Confrontation%3A%20How%20Will%20The%2018th%20Lok%20Sabha%20Function%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2F7ko6i7hc_new-parliament-ani-new-lok-sabha-ani_625x300_01_July_23.jpg%3Fim%3DResize%3D(1230%3Fim%3DFaceCrop%3Fim%3DFaceCrop%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20scorching%20heat%20has%20somewhat%20abated%2C%20but%20monsoon%20clouds%20remain%20far%20from%20New%20Delhi.%20Stormy%20conditions%20are%20clearly%20discernible%20as%20the%2018th%20Lok%20Sabha%20begins%20its%20session%20on%20June%2024.%20Never%20before%20has%20the%20appointment%20of%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwho-is-bhartruhari-mahtab-the-pro-tem-speaker-for-18th-lok-sabha-5956738%5C%22%3ESpeaker%20%3Cem%3EPro-tem%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20conventional%20post%20replicated%20from%20the%20Westminster%20system%2C%20generated%20such%20controversy.%20The%20Opposition's%20objection%20to%20the%20appointment%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fparliament-session-pro-tem-speaker-pro-tem-speaker-big-bjp-vs-india-flashpoint-as-18th-lok-sabha-meets-today-5956134%5C%22%3EBhartruhari%20Mahtab%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20who%20has%20continuously%20served%20as%20a%20Lok%20Sabha%20member%20for%20seven%20terms%20since%201998%2C%20signals%20potential%20conflicts%20ahead.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EPro-tem%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3Eis%20a%20Latin%20phrase%20meaning%20%26quot%3Bfor%20the%20time%20being%26quot%3B.%20The%20term%20of%20the%20previous%20Lok%20Sabha%20Speaker%20ends%20a%20day%20before%20the%20new%20House%20is%20constituted.%20The%20President%20of%20India%2C%20under%20Article%2095(1)%2C%20appoints%20a%20senior%20member%20as%20Speaker%20Pro-tem%2C%20who%20is%20administered%20the%20oath%20by%20the%20President%20and%20tasked%20with%20the%20duties%20of%20the%20Speaker%20until%20a%20new%20Speaker%20is%20elected.%20Assisted%20by%20a%20panel%20of%20senior%20MPs%2C%20the%20Speaker%20Pro-tem%20administers%20the%20oath%20to%20new%20MPs%2C%20setting%20the%20stage%20for%20the%20election%20of%20a%20new%20Speaker.%20The%20oath%20administration%20is%20scheduled%20for%20July%2024-25%2C%20followed%20by%20the%20election%20of%20the%20Speaker%20and%20Deputy%20Speaker%20as%20envisaged%20in%20Article%2093%20on%20July%2026.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EConsensus%20May%20Not%20Come%20Easy%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHistorically%2C%20the%20Speaker%20and%20Deputy%20Speaker%20have%20been%20elected%20by%20consensus.%20However%2C%20there%20are%20indications%20that%20the%2018th%20Lok%20Sabha%20may%20witness%20contested%20elections%20for%20these%20posts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwho-is-bhartruhari-mahtab-the-pro-tem-speaker-for-18th-lok-sabha-5956738%5C%22%3EAlso%20Read%20%7C%C2%A0Who%20Is%20Bhartruhari%20Mahtab%2C%20The%20Pro-Tem%20Speaker%20For%2018th%20Lok%20Sabha%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fparliament-session-pro-tem-speaker-pro-tem-speaker-big-bjp-vs-india-flashpoint-as-18th-lok-sabha-meets-today-5956134%5C%22%3EThe%20Opposition%20favoured%20Kodikunnil%20Suresh%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20Congress%20MP%20from%20Kerala%20who%20has%20been%20elected%20eight%20times%20since%20his%20first%20election%20in%201989.%20The%20government%20argues%20that%20Suresh%20had%20lost%20elections%20in%201998%20and%202004%2C%20unlike%20Mahtab%2C%20whose%20unbroken%20record%20of%20victories%20since%201998%20spans%20seven%20terms.%20Mahtab%2C%20currently%20in%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%2C%20was%20a%20member%20of%20the%20Biju%20Janata%20Dal%20(BJD)%20in%20the%20previous%20House.%20Suresh%20served%20as%20the%20Congress's%20chief%20whip%20in%20the%2017th%20Lok%20Sabha.%20Additionally%2C%20Mahtab's%20father%2C%20Harekrushna%20Mahtab%2C%20known%20as%20'Utkal%20Keshari'%2C%20was%20Orissa's%20(now%20Odisha)%20first%20Chief%20Minister%20in%201946%20and%20later%20served%20as%20Governor%20of%20the%20composite%20state%20of%20Bombay%20(now%20Maharashtra%20and%20Gujarat)%20in%201955-56.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EParliamentary%20Affairs%20Ministers%20In%20The%20Past%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20primary%20responsibility%20for%20the%20smooth%20functioning%20of%20the%20Houses%20of%20Parliament%20lies%20with%20the%20ruling%20party%2C%20with%20the%20Parliamentary%20Affairs%20Minister%20assuming%20a%20key%20role.%20Notable%20figures%20such%20as%20Satya%20Narain%20Sinha%2C%20who%20set%20precedents%20for%20consensus%20building%20in%20his%20initial%2018%20years%20of%20service%2C%20and%20later%2C%20leaders%20like%20Ram%20Subhag%20Singh%20(the%20first%20recognised%20Leader%20of%20Opposition%20during%20the%201969%20split)%2C%20K.%20Raghuramiah%20(known%20for%20his%20consultations%20with%20Opposition%20MPs%20and%20dubbed%20the%20'minister%20for%20Opposition')%2C%20Bhishma%20Narain%20Singh%2C%20Buta%20Singh%2C%20H.K.L.%20Bhagat%2C%20V.C.%20Shukla%2C%20and%20Ghulam%20Nabi%20Azad%20(who%20became%20LoP%20in%20Rajya%20Sabha%20and%20on%20whose%20retirement%20Narendra%20Modi's%20tribute%20created%20parliamentary%20history)%20served%20as%20the%20Parliamentary%20Affairs%20ministers%20during%20the%20Congress%20era.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fvideo%2Fwill-protest-bjp-mp-s-appointment-as-pro-tem-speaker-congress-k-suresh-806839%5C%22%3EWatch%20%7C%C2%A0%26quot%3BWill%20Protest%20BJP%20MP's%20Appointment%20As%20Pro-Tem%20Speaker%26quot%3B%3A%20Congress'%20K%20Suresh%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPramod%20Mahajan%20was%20the%20first%20BJP%20leader%20to%20hold%20this%20post%2C%20navigating%20it%20well%20despite%20his%20party%20lacking%20a%20majority.%20He%20was%20followed%20by%20P.%20Rangarajan%20Kumaramangalam%2C%20M.L.%20Khurana%2C%20Sushma%20Swaraj%2C%20Venkaiah%20Naidu%2C%20and%20Ananth%20Kumar%2C%20preceding%20Narendra%20Tomar%20and%20Pralhad%20Joshi%2C%20whose%20tenures%20witnessed%20a%20diminished%20rapport%20between%20the%20government%20and%20Opposition%20benches%20compared%20to%20earlier%20times.%20Now%2C%20it's%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpro-tem-speaker-bhartruhari-mahtab-kodikunnil-suresh-kiren-rijiju-in-pro-tem-speaker-row-kiren-rijiju-slams-congress-says-am-ashamed-5939648%5C%22%3EKiren%20Rijiju%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20member%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20since%202004%20who%20began%20his%20career%20on%20the%20Opposition%20benches%2C%20who%20faces%20a%20daunting%20task%20as%20the%20Parliamentary%20Affairs%20Minister%20in%20the%2018th%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20where%20the%20ruling%20party%20is%20short%20of%20an%20absolute%20majority.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20LoP%20Question%20Facing%20The%20House%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20an%20election%20is%20held%20for%20the%20post%20of%20Speaker%2C%20it%20may%20lead%20to%20acrimony.%20Unlike%20the%2016th%20and%2017th%20Lok%20Sabhas%2C%20the%2018th%20one%20will%20have%20a%20recognised%20Leader%20of%20Opposition%20(LoP).%20Although%20elected%20with%20much%20fanfare%20by%20his%20party%20a%20fortnight%20ago%2C%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20has%20yet%20to%20indicate%20if%20he%20will%20assume%20this%20key%20role.%20Sources%20within%20the%20Congress%20suggest%20he%20prefers%20Gaurav%20Gogoi%2C%20who%20served%20as%20Deputy%20Leader%20of%20the%20Congress%20in%20the%20previous%20House%2C%20for%20the%20position.%20His%20argument%20is%20that%20with%20Sonia%20Gandhi%2C%20a%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%2C%20serving%20as%20the%20chairperson%20of%20the%20Congress%20Party%20in%20Parliament%20(CPP)%2C%20the%20BJP's%20criticism%20of%20'dynastic%20politics'%20('%3Cem%3Eparivarwaad%3C%2Fem%3E')%20against%20the%20Congress%20would%20gain%20traction%20if%20he%20were%20to%20become%20LoP.%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20reportedly%20wants%20Haryana%20MP%20Kumari%20Selja%2C%20a%20Dalit%20leader%2C%20to%20assume%20the%20role.%20Party%20chief%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20is%20inclined%20to%20support%20Chandigarh%20MP%20Manish%20Tewari%2C%20a%20third-term%20MP%20who%20has%20held%20key%20organisational%20roles%20and%20has%20demonstrated%20his%20legal%20acumen%20in%20House%20debates%2C%20should%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20decline.%20The%20name%20of%20fourth-term%20Thiruvananthapuram%20MP%20Shashi%20Tharoor%2C%20who%20unsuccessfully%20vied%20as%20India's%20candidate%20for%20the%20United%20Nations%20Secretary-General%20in%202006%2C%20is%20also%20doing%20the%20rounds%20in%20Congress%20circles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20the%20Speaker%20and%20the%20LoP%20will%20play%20pivotal%20roles%20in%20the%20smooth%20functioning%20of%20the%2018th%20Lok%20Sabha.%20The%20LoP%20is%20a%20member%20of%20crucial%20selection%20panels%20where%20fostering%20a%20positive%20rapport%20between%20the%20government%20and%20the%20Opposition%20is%20essential.%20Acrimony%20arising%20from%20the%20election%20of%20the%20Speaker%20or%20the%20role%20of%20the%20LoP%20could%20cast%20a%20shadow%2C%20underscoring%20the%20importance%20of%20achieving%20consensus%20rather%20than%20confrontation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Opposition's%20Condition%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2017th%20Lok%20Sabha%20did%20not%20have%20a%20Deputy%20Speaker.%20Article%2093%20stipulates%20that%20two%20members%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20will%20be%20elected%20as%20Speaker%20and%20Deputy%20Speaker.%20According%20to%20Article%2094%2C%20if%20the%20Speaker%20wishes%20to%20resign%2C%20they%20must%20tender%20their%20resignation%20to%20the%20Deputy%20Speaker.%20During%20the%20Constituent%20Assembly%20debates%2C%20there%20was%20deliberation%20over%20whether%20the%20Speaker's%20resignation%20should%20be%20addressed%20to%20the%20President%20of%20India%3B%20it%20was%20decided%20that%20since%20the%20House%20was%20the%20appointing%20authority%2C%20the%20power%20to%20accept%20the%20Speaker's%20resignation%20should%20lie%20with%20the%20Deputy%20Speaker.%20Thus%2C%20the%2017th%20Lok%20Sabha%20had%20an%20anomaly%2C%20with%20the%20position%20remaining%20vacant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Opposition%20has%20conditioned%20the%20consensus%20on%20the%20election%20of%20the%20Speaker%20in%20the%2018th%20Lok%20Sabha%20on%20the%20Deputy%20Speaker%20position%20being%20given%20to%20a%20non-ruling%20alliance%20member.%20The%20upcoming%20week%20is%20crucial%2C%20as%20whether%20consensus%20evolves%20or%20confrontation%20ensues%20will%20shape%20the%20functioning%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20in%20the%20days%20ahead.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Shubhabrata%20Bhattacharya%20is%20a%20retired%20editor%20and%20a%20public%20affairs%20commentator)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719216360000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2F7ko6i7hc_new-parliament-ani-new-lok-sabha-ani_625x300_01_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fconsensus-or-confrontation-how-will-the-18th-lok-sabha-function-5957554%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Historically%2C%20the%20Speaker%20and%20Deputy%20Speaker%20have%20been%20elected%20by%20consensus.%20However%2C%20there%20are%20indications%20that%20the%2018th%20Lok%20Sabha%20may%20witness%20contests%20for%20these%20posts.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fconsensus-or-confrontation-how-will-the-18th-lok-sabha-function-5957554%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fconsensus-or-confrontation-how-will-the-18th-