sider.com%2Fspain-scrapping-golden-visas-real-estate-investment-wealthy-foreigners-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Escrapped%20%26quot%3Bgolden%20visas%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20non-EU%20nationals%2C%20saying%20the%20visa%20program%20was%20adding%20to%20housing-supply%20pressures.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20critics%20say%20the%20Barcelona%20ban%20will%20do%20little%20to%20change%20the%20rental%20climate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20opposition%20politician%20Dami%C3%A0%20Calvet%20said%20that%20not%20all%2010%2C000%20homes%20would%20go%20back%20on%20the%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPretending%20that%20all%2010%2C000%20will%20have%20a%20residential%20use%20is%20not%20realistic%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.spanishpropertyinsight.com%2F2024%2F06%2F22%2Fbarcelona-announces-radical-step-of-banning-all-tourist-rentals-but-the-housing-crisis-will-only-get-worse%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elocal%20media%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Calvet%20said%20not%20all%20homes%20with%20licenses%20were%20actually%20rented%20out%20to%20tourists%2C%20with%20many%20owners%20keeping%20the%20license%20just%20to%20add%20value%20to%20the%20property%20in%20case%20they%20wanted%20to%20sell%20down%20the%20line.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTourist%20apartments%20represent%20just%200.77%25%20of%20Barcelona's%20housing%20stock%2C%26quot%3B%20Enrique%20Alc%C3%A1ntara%2C%20the%20president%20of%20the%20Barcelona%20Tourist%20Apartments%20Association%2C%20told%20media%20after%20the%20announcement.%20%26quot%3BAll%20it%20will%20do%20is%20increase%20the%20number%20of%20illegal%20tourist%20rentals%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2259b31b74-4a4c-47db-a07b-71df21bb1eca%5C%22%3EGlobal%20short-term%20rental%20restrictions%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20cities%20are%20similarly%20eyeing%20short-term%20rental%20restrictions%20to%20manage%20skyrocketing%20housing%20costs%20in%20what's%20been%20deemed%20the%20%26quot%3BAirbnb%20effect.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3