or%20your%20initiative%2C%E2%80%9D%20Neenu%20shares%20in%20a%20conversation%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere%20is%20her%20journey%20from%20looking%20for%20her%20passion%20to%20becoming%20a%20social%20entrepreneur%20who%20has%20helped%20over%206%2C000%20stakeholders%20including%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F334179%2Fteenage-changemakers-of-india-children-founders-of-startups-ngos-inspiring%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Echangemakers%2C%20NGOs%20and%20corporates%2C%20bring%20social%20change%20%3C%2Fa%3Eby%20raising%20funds%2C%20securing%20the%20right%20connections%20and%20reaching%20the%20people%20who%20need%20help.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EChoosing%20the%20road%20less%20taken%20%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERaised%20in%20Kerala%2C%20Neenu%20was%20not%20sure%20what%20she%20wanted%20to%20do%2C%20so%20she%20decided%20to%20go%20for%20a%20professional%20degree.%20%E2%80%9CAt%20that%20time%2C%20I%20was%20not%20sure%20what%20to%20take%20up%20in%20college%2C%20so%20I%20went%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F343321%2Frahul-arepaka-harvested-robotics-hyderabad-ai-startup-laser-weeder-robot-help-farmers-earn-more%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eahead%20with%20engineering%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I%20even%20went%20on%20to%20get%20a%20masters%20in%20the%20same%20field%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20Neenu%20was%20among%20her%20peers%20who%20were%20passionate%20about%20engineering%2C%20she%20realised%20that%20she%20was%20a%20misfit%20in%20the%20group.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20realised%20how%20I%20was%20not%20here%20because%20of%20my%20passion%20but%20just%20for%20a%20degree.%20The%20crisis%20of%20not%20knowing%20what%20I%20wanted%20to%20do%20with%20my%20life%20kicked%20in%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5